// Adaptable — Supabase project configuration.
//
// This points the native app at the SAME Supabase project as the web app
// (ypziulvtfsyrwpotlevp), so recipes, votes, comments and the community
// feed are shared across web, iOS and Android. The anon key is a
// publishable client key — every table enforces Row Level Security — so
// committing it here is safe (see README "Security notes").
//
// Leave both values blank to boot the app in Demo Mode (seeded local
// data, no network) — handy for UI work without a backend.

